						<summary>

						<p>This begins with the <hi rend="italic">birudas</hi> of the Vijayanagar kings, but the name of the king is lost. It is also unfinished. It seems to record the appointment of a stone-mason by the temple authorities (with the grant of some land for his living).</p>						

